    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 assessment matrix for a Class II device. Discretization error and numerical solver error achieved levels above requirement, providing additional confidence. The model form factor was evaluated through a thorough qualitative review by domain experts and an independent reviewer, confirming adequacy for the CPB hemolysis COU. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the Accepted decision for use of the CFD model to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions and confirm RH < 1 relative to the predicate device.",
